## Endpoints

- `POST /rpc` - RPC endpoint for queries, mutations, actions
- `GET /health` - Health check
- `GET /ready` - Readiness check (database connectivity)
- `GET /_dashboard` - Admin dashboard
- `WS /ws` - WebSocket for real-time subscriptions
